[normal]10[bold].[bold]              [bold]C[bold]ompetitive landscape [bold]&#xa0;
[normal]10
[normal].1
[normal]              
[normal]The UK
[normal]’s expertise in oil and gas gives us a huge national advantage.  Government and industry 
[normal]are 
[normal]working together to keep the UK at the heart of the global race in the worldwide energy industry, creating jobs and growth.
