[normal]Oil &amp; Gas Industrial Strategy
[normal] 
[normal]was d
[normal]evelope
[normal]d in partnership with industry.  It
[normal] sets out a clear path to exploit the UK’s remaining resources and overcome an increasingly challenging production environment.
