[normal]              
[normal]Since publication, the Oil &amp;
[normal] Gas Industry Council, supported by a BIS-led secretariat, has begun taking forward the actions listed in the strategy. Several have already been completed, and a number of key milestones are due to be finalised by the end of this year. One of the key deli
[normal]verables – a research project mapping the UK supply chain, including exports, by value and destination, to determine areas of constraint and potential opportunities for additional support – is now underway.
