[normal]In addition, 
[normal]DECC commissioned an Oil and 
[normal]Gas Review
[normal] 
[normal]in June 2013
[normal].  This is be
[normal]ing led by Sir Ian Wood, who is
[normal] looking in depth at the key issues which need to be addressed to ensure
[normal] the
[normal] longevity of the industry and our resources.  
